        <!-- Release notes (keep it brief) -->
        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.19 - Prevent Navigation Reload Loops</h3>

            <h4>Improvements</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Clear sessionStorage immediately to prevent infinite reload loops</li>
                <li>Single direct navigation attempt at 2s (instead of multiple)</li>
                <li>Check if already at target slide before navigating</li>
                <li>Direct Storyline API only - no reload-based navigation</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Technical Details</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Uses goToSlide() or GetPlayer().SetVar('Jump') methods</li>
                <li>Relies on suspend_data modification for initial navigation</li>
                <li>Direct API call is fallback only if suspend_data didn't work</li>
                <li>Prevents modifySuspendDataAndReload calls in fallback path</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Versions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.18: Enhanced resume field modification + fallback</li>
                <li>v2.0.17: Intercept suspend_data writes to prevent revert</li>
                <li>v2.0.16: URL-based slide navigation (?slide=X) for embed</li>
                <li>v2.0.15: LMSGetValue interception for navigation</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
        </releasenotes>
    </update>
